  "description": "The Siemens refrigerator is made of the French-door type (hinged), equipped with four doors and a freezer divided into two chambers. Its total volume reaches an impressive 605 liters, so the model is suitable for a large family. The manufacturer paid special attention to performance and energy efficiency. The multiAirflow cooling system distributes air evenly in the refrigerator compartment, ensures constant temperatures at all levels, regulates temperature and humidity levels and eliminates the accumulation of condensation. The intelligent inverter compressor adjusts the temperature of the refrigerator according to indoor and outdoor conditions, operating at the optimal speed. Its main advantages are stable and efficient operation, durability and low noise level (38 dB). No Frost technology prevents the formation of ice and eliminates the need to manually defrost the refrigerator and freezer compartments. Siemens KF96NAXEA is equipped with a large number of different shelves and containers for storing food and utensils with food. The refrigerator compartment offers a separate zone with its own supply of cold air and a temperature of 0 degrees for storing meat and fish, as well as an area with an optimal level of humidity for fruits, vegetables and herbs. Also useful are the Super Cool and Express Freeze functions, which use lower temperatures to quickly cool food. There are two options for control: using a touch panel with LED display and via the Internet. The refrigerator syncs with the Home Connect mobile app and allows remote control via a smartphone. In addition, users will appreciate interior LED lighting, hidden door handles and an indicator that signals when the door is not closed.",
